To install the OpenVPN-ALS LDAP authentication module, do the following:

* Run "ant install" in $OVPNALS_HOME
* Run "ant install" in this directory.
* Copy the build/release/ovpnals-community-ldap.zip to $OVPNALS_HOME/ovpnals/conf/repository/archives
* Re-run "ant install" in $OVPNALS_HOME
* Select LDAP for the user database in the install phase (see Installing and running OpenVPN-ALS server in 
Wiki)
